## Recovery
- If uncertain about user intent: ask one targeted clarifying question.
- Resume from the last confirmed user-facing conversation stage.
- Never resume from hidden execution state or internal service state.
- If Workflow Brain is active and context is lost: restart from CLARIFYING.

